1117:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         value for HSE crystal.
1118:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *
